msg: SLING-2501 Apply patch by Dragos Dascalita Haut (thank you very much)

author: stefan2
msg: Reduce FSFS open latency. This patch prevents the creation
of temporary error objects in read_format when the format
file exists. To that end, we simply read the whole file into a
string buffer and parse it from there.
(read_format): Read the whole file and *then* parse it
